info.title: YouTube Transcript API
info.description: API for retrieving transcripts of YouTube videos in XML format.

get.summary: Retrieve the transcript of a specified YouTube video
get.description: Returns the transcript for a YouTube video based on the video ID in XML format.

parameters.name: videoid
parameters.description: The ID of the YouTube video

parameters.name: page
parameters.description: The page number of the transcript to retrieve, default is 1

get.summary: Search for YouTube videos by keyword
get.description: Returns a list of YouTube videos matching the specified keyword.

parameters.name: keyword
parameters.description: The search keyword for YouTube videos

200.description: Successful response with list of videos

get.summary: Get the latest videos by channel ID
get.description: Returns the latest videos for a specified YouTube channel ID.

parameters.name: channelId
parameters.description: The ID of the YouTube channel

200.description: Successful response with list of latest videos
